<td valign="middle">
<b>New!</b> PDB Deposition switches to mmCIF format on the 1st of July 2019.
Deposition files in mmCIF format can be generated using
<a href="deposition_ccp4i2">CCP4i2</a> or
<a href="deposition_ccp4cloud">CCP4Cloud</a>
</td>
</tr>
